Project Title: Local Business & Startup Directory (Flask Web App)
Submitted by: Bello yamusa
Description:
This project is a simple web application built using Python and Flask. It allows users to add and view local businesses and startups in a directory. Each listing includes the business name, category, location, and contact information. The application demonstrates basic web development concepts such as routing, form handling, and data display.
Features:
Add new businesses or startups
View all business listings
Display business details (name, category, location, contact)
Instructions to Run:
Install Flask: pip install flask
Run the app: python app.py
Open browser and go to: http://127.0.0.1:5000
